Nette Packages
**************

Nette is a full-stack PHP framework composed from a set of decoupled and reusable packages.
You can use any of these packages standalone, independently from the rest of framework.

You can download each package from [official Git repository |https://github.com/nette].
The recommended way how to install them is via [Composer |doc:composer].
For instance, to install the [Latte |https://latte.nette.org] use:

```shell
composer require latte/latte
```

Names of other packages are in the third column in the table below.

Complete framework (i.e. all packages) can be added using:

```shell
composer require nette/nette
```


